  stimulus_text = 'The text emphasizes that it is important to be aware of how the different sources of information can affect the way we see the world. The text states that one way to ensure that sources of information are trustworthy is to check their accuracy, but it also suggests that there are other factors to consider.  For example, the text suggests that we should also think about the author’s motivations and potential biases.  Which choice best represents the main idea of this passage?',
